50 SECTION 3.
51 This Act shall become effective on July 1, 2026, only if it is determined to have been
52 concurrently funded as provided in Chapter 20 of Title 47 of the Official Code of Georgia
53 Annotated, the "Public Retirement Systems Standards Law"; otherwise, this Act shall not
54 become effective and shall be automatically repealed in its entirety on July 1, 2026, as
55 required by subsection (a) of Code Section 47-20-50.
56 SECTION 4.
57 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
